{"tid":910365,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【趣blogblog】全港最top 1%打工仔賺幾多？（股榮）","createTime":"2018-11-21T06:33:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-21T12:28:11.000Z","uid":57424,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"332d6202ca5f9a18e7414fe3c97b38486da52eea","tid":910365,"uid":57424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T06:33:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181121/58938392\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181121%2F58938392&d=3epJlx%2FWQLZ2qb6f%2B2woDBxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=cb0f0647\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181121%2F58938392&h=039dc052\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181121/58938392</a><br />\n又到銀行推出稅貸及交稅季節，近數年稅務局已取消公布打工皇帝數據，但稅務局年報，附表仍有全港打工仔收入及交稅資料，值得與各位分享。<br />\n根據2016至17年度，全港合共有176.4萬打工仔要交稅，交稅最多的一個組別是年薪介乎30至40萬元（約月薪2.5萬至3.3萬元）的打工仔，人數達29萬，佔比為16.5%，平均每人交稅3,100元。<br />\n要做到全港打工仔收入最高的一成，年薪最少要100萬元以上，人數接近16萬人，交稅最少要11萬元，這班人，某程度就是銀行稅貸終極目標。<br />\n邊組貢獻全港最多稅款，答案不是年薪千萬，而是年收入介乎100萬以上至150萬的一組「窮中產」，這組8.27萬名打工仔，合共交稅95.35億元，每人平均交11.5萬元稅。<br />\n至於要成為全港最top 1% 打工仔，年薪則最少要300萬元以上（月薪最少25萬元），年賺300萬以上至500萬元打工仔有1.31萬個（0.74%）、年賺500萬以上至750萬打工仔有4,211個（0.24%），年賺750萬以上至1000萬打工仔有1,641個（0.09%），年賺千萬以上有2,440個(0.14%）。<br />\n<br />\n連登仔有人數達16萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab597c5098ce9eb29d026d959e23a4abc7922fa7","tid":910365,"uid":181418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T06:45:23.000Z","msg":"連登仔：隨隨便便都交十零萬稅啦"},{"pid":"b4391bfd26801ecdfb1d1c8400a9a3dc5e9f911a","tid":910365,"uid":57424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab597c5098ce9eb29d026d959e23a4abc7922fa7","tid":910365,"uid":181418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T06:45:23.000Z","msg":"連登仔：隨隨便便都交十零萬稅啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T06:46:38.000Z","msg":"散紙"},{"pid":"93f01b4898b056d67a004d112435dd1116152663","tid":910365,"uid":129340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T11:04:12.000Z","msg":"慘 諗下人地自己生意用財技交少幾多稅<br />\n再諗下你年年比人屈左10幾% 去起人工島<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雖然比起歐美稅率係好低"},{"pid":"ac74117e5c97bb471182b0d0c4b3c65d754a59b6","tid":910365,"uid":30615,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T11:34:12.000Z","msg":"其實普遍香港人交嘅薪俸稅加埋只佔港府每年1% 嘅收入 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8745583b851da69b929a5cbb55be2b4054740b30","tid":910365,"uid":57424,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ac74117e5c97bb471182b0d0c4b3c65d754a59b6","tid":910365,"uid":30615,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T11:34:12.000Z","msg":"其實普遍香港人交嘅薪俸稅加埋只佔港府每年1% 嘅收入 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T11:59:50.000Z","msg":"係窮人生上搵錢係樂趣黎嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f9faf0a4e5b132d488e8e1394de59afd8fde9f5","tid":910365,"uid":163207,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T12:23:17.000Z","msg":"所以懞鳩青山道整假糧單都要整夠三十萬?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6f27ab601ef3487323b616d79fdab67ce39b6cb","tid":910365,"uid":37599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T12:28:11.000Z","msg":"屌，年薪百萬叫窮中產<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}